<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Explore the Bookstore</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        header nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        header nav ul li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        header nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        header nav ul li a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        /* Main Section Styles */
        main {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        main img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            display: block;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        /* Product Styles */
        .product {
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .product img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        .product h3 {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .product p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }

        .product .price {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e67e22;
        }

        /* Gallery Styles */
        div.gallery {
            margin: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            float: left;
            width: 180px;
        }

        div.gallery:hover {
            border: 1px solid #777;
        }

        div.gallery img {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
        }

        div.desc {
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* Footer Styles */
        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            bottom: 0;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header nav ul {
                text-align: center;
            }

            header nav ul li {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            main img {
                max-width: 100%;
            }

            div.gallery {
                width: 100%;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .product {
                width: calc(100% - 40px);
                margin: 10px auto;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Explore the Bookstore</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#gallery">Gallery</a></li>
                <li><a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Home Section -->
    <section id="home">
        <main>
            <h2>Featured Books</h2>
            <div class="product">
           
                <h3>The Great Gatsby</h3>
                <p>by F. Scott Fitzgerald</p>
                <p>A classic novel set in the Jazz Age, exploring themes of wealth, love, and the American Dream.</p>
                <p class="price">$10.99</p>
            </div>

            <!-- New Image Section -->
            <h2>Book Cover</h2>
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Book Cover" width="500" height="333">

            <!-- New Image Section 2 -->
            <h2>Books in the Store</h2>
            <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Books in Store" width="500" height="333">
        </main>
    </section>
</body>
</html>
